      "title": "Sri Lanka\u2019s Dhammika Perera sworn in as Minister of Investment Promotion",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "ECONOMYNEXT \u2013 Sri Lankan business tycoon Dhammika Perera, who recently entered parliament on the ruling Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna (SLPP) national list, has been appointed Minister of Investment Promotion.",
        "Perera was sworn in before President Gotabaya Rajapaksa Friday June 24 evening, the president\u2019s office said.",
        "Perera entered parliament mid June replacing former Finance Minister Basil Rajapaksa on the SLPP national list. (Colombo/Jun24/2022)"
      ],
